message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and music processing. cs.AI is also likely as it deals with artificial intelligence and machine learning, which are used in the paper. cs.SI is another possible category as it deals with signal processing and information theory, which are relevant to the Maximum Entropy models used. cs.LG is also possible as it deals with machine learning and statistical models. cs.HC is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses a listening test, which could fall under the category of human-computer interaction.
